 \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bigham will make his Olympic debut aged 32 when the track cycling starts on Monday, riding alongside Ethan Hayter, Charlie Tanfield and Ollie Wood in the pursuit after taking one of the more unusual paths to this point.\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ethan Hayter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\"}, {\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Tanfield\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlie Tanfield\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Tanfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Tanfield\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic debut\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"the track cycling\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"Ollie Wood\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"the pursuit\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"the more unusual paths\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An aerodynamics specialist who used to work forMercedes F1, Bigham admits he is not the most physiologically gifted athlete but he uses his engineering skills to push the envelope - and not just for himself.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An aerodynamics specialist\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"forMercedes F1\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"the most physiologically gifted athlete\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"his engineering skills\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the envelope\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022, Bigham broke the prestigious Hour Record on the track, only to then help his Ineos Grenadiers team-mate Filippo Ganna better it two months later.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos Grenadiers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\"}, {\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Filippo Ganna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"the prestigious Hour Record\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"better it\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After butting heads with the previous coaching regime within Team GB, Bigham went to the Tokyo Olympics as an advisor toDenmark- who took silver as Britain, reigning Olympic champions since 2008, crashed out in the first round and finished seventh.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999975460776209, \"rank\": 2.45350510559869e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.5634121564248982, \"rank\": 0.7748663606259013, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heads\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous coaching regime\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"an advisor\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"toDenmark-\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champions\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bigham long ago felt his own opportunity to ride at the very highest level had gone, butBritish Cyclinghave welcomed him back.\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"his own opportunity\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"the very highest level\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"butBritish Cyclinghave\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022, he was part of the team that won the team pursuit world title at the Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines velodrome that will host this week's racing.\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"world title\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"the Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines velodrome\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"this week's racing\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It means a lot of different things,\\\" Bigham said of earning Olympic selection.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"different things\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic selection\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The key thing was that justification for the decisions I have made.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The key thing\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"that justification\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"the decisions\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I have attracted criticism or had people turn their eyes up a bit about the decisions I have made and how I have gone about my path.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"their eyes\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"the decisions\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"my path\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest I have felt the same sometimes and some of that criticism is probably justified but it's nice to be in a situation where you feel welcome, you feel you have made the right steps to get here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that criticism\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"a situation\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"the right steps\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bigham was the mastermind behind the Huub-Wattbike trade team that emerged after the Rio Olympics and challenged the thinking at British Cycling, regularly beating them in competition.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2328, \"entities\": [{\"begi