tting on the bike.\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's where people like Filippo Ganna come into the equation and make it a bigger thing than just me trying to maximise my own performance but it becomes about trying to create one of the best performances in history.\\\"\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2700, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Filippo Ganna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"the equation\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2736}, {\"ngram\": \"my own performance\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"the best performances\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the opportunity in front of him now, Bigham has had to be selfish.\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2925}, {\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His former employers Denmark are major rivals.\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2989, \"end\": 2996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.8851777153403404, \"rank\": 0.12791707798742233, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His former employers\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2988}, {\"ngram\": \"major rivals\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ganna anchors the Italian squad that took gold in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3065, \"end\": 3070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9994752150626646, \"rank\": 0.0005219058917504085, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ganna anchors\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"the Italian squad\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italy did so in a world record time of three minutes 42.032 seconds, more than two seconds faster than the record time of 3:44.672 set by Denmark at the 2020 world championships.\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3073, \"end\": 3078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9960077629039312, \"rank\": 0.00210173413535807, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3211, \"end\": 3218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.8851777153403404, \"rank\": 0.12791707798742233, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a world record time\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"three minutes\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3125}, {\"ngram\": \"42.032 seconds\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"the record time\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 world championships\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bigham, who is never without a spreadsheet to analyse such things, believes that record could be broken inParisbut added that the atmospherics in Izu - a velodrome at altitude and with high humidity - was key to the fast pace three years ago.\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"a spreadsheet\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"analyse\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"such things\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3318}, {\"ngram\": \"record\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmospherics\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"Izu\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3402}, {\"ngram\": \"a velodrome\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3416}, {\"ngram\": \"altitude\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3428}, {\"ngram\": \"high humidity\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"the fast pace\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what it would take to win gold, Bigham said: \\\"I do not believe the jump will be quite so big (as in Tokyo).\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3603, \"end\": 3608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9994752150626646, \"rank\": 0.0005219058917504085, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3533}, {\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"the jump\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But even so I'd be pretty confident you are going to have to fight for a world record in the final if you want to win.\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a world record\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's a world record or thereabouts.\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3773, \"